1432
01:29:17,135 --> 01:29:18,343
(Nick exhales deeply)

1433
01:29:18,343 --> 01:29:20,626
(upbeat jazz music)

1434
01:29:20,626 --> 01:29:22,088
- Congratulations, hon.

1435
01:29:22,088 --> 01:29:23,921
- [Claudia] Thank you.

1436
01:29:28,381 --> 01:29:31,048
(Claudia gasps)

1437
01:29:36,384 --> 01:29:39,051
(both laughing)

1438
01:29:53,490 --> 01:29:54,323
- Kit.

1439
01:29:59,248 --> 01:30:00,081
- Are you okay?

1440
01:30:02,878 --> 01:30:04,910
- I can't sleep, it's too hot.

1441
01:30:07,840 --> 01:30:10,000
- Me neither, what should we do?

1442
01:30:11,210 --> 01:30:14,020
- I don't know.

1443
01:30:14,020 --> 01:30:18,710
Well, my school's having a
Halloween Ball this year,

1444
01:30:18,710 --> 01:30:21,135
