1450
01:30:45,200 --> 01:30:46,787
One, two, three.

1451
01:30:46,787 --> 01:30:48,455
One, two, three.

1452
01:30:48,455 --> 01:30:50,039
One, two, three.

1453
01:30:50,039 --> 01:30:51,948
Good, one, two, three.

1454
01:30:51,948 --> 01:30:53,292
One, two, three.

1455
01:30:53,292 --> 01:30:56,823
That's good, good.

1456
01:30:56,823 --> 01:30:58,870
Look up, look up.

