1465
01:31:19,698 --> 01:31:20,876
Wanna go faster?

1466
01:31:20,876 --> 01:31:21,772
- [Joshua] Okay.

1467
01:31:21,772 --> 01:31:22,870
- A little faster.

1468
01:31:22,870 --> 01:31:24,730
Ready, now make a square.

1469
01:31:25,639 --> 01:31:28,222
(Kit laughing)

1470
01:31:31,058 --> 01:31:33,040
- Tell me a joke, you
don't know any jokes?

1471
01:31:33,040 --> 01:31:33,873
- Nah.

1472
01:31:33,873 --> 01:31:35,510
- Nah, don't you hear them in school?

1473
01:31:36,400 --> 01:31:37,233
- [Joshua] No.

1474
01:31:37,233 --> 01:31:38,066
- [Kit] Hey look, Josh.

1475
01:31:38,066 --> 01:31:38,970
- [Joshua] Oh neat.

1476
01:31:38,970 --> 01:31:40,720
- We could hang these.

1477
01:31:40,720 --> 01:31:42,090
