1478
01:31:42,090 --> 01:31:42,931
- [Joshua] You.

1479
01:31:42,931 --> 01:31:44,638
- [Kit] Yeah (laughs).

1480
01:31:44,638 --> 01:31:46,088
Some of these are great.

1481
01:31:46,088 --> 01:31:46,921
- Yeah.

