01:32:18,180 --> 01:32:19,597
Can I go in, Mom?

1484
01:32:21,798 --> 01:32:22,631
- Yeah.

1485
01:32:28,466 --> 01:32:29,466
- Thank you.

1486
01:32:37,311 --> 01:32:39,267
- There you go.

1487
01:32:39,267 --> 01:32:42,267
