Thanksgiving vacation with him.

1500
01:33:15,400 --> 01:33:16,820
- [Claudia] Oh, that sounds like fun.

1501
01:33:16,820 --> 01:33:17,653
- Yeah.

1502
01:33:17,653 --> 01:33:22,640
- You know, I almost called
you to tell you about the book.

1503
01:33:23,610 --> 01:33:26,909
I even thought about trying
to see you one last time.

1504
01:33:26,909 --> 01:33:28,289
- It's okay, Claude,

1505
01:33:28,289 --> 01:33:32,113
I'm just glad we were
walking by and I saw you.

1506
01:33:32,113 --> 01:33:33,170
- Me too.

1507
01:33:33,170 --> 01:33:34,807
- Now your book came out.

1508
01:33:34,807 --> 01:33:36,724
- Mm mm, it's our book.

